Given A Mutiple Choice Question View
And A Multiple Choice Question Revision
And Revision Content is "After 1 is ..."
And Revision Choices are 1,2,3,4
When Revision is bound to View
Then text of labelQuestion is "After 1 is ..."
And 4 buttons of text 1,2,3,4 are added to panelChoices
When User click 1st button of panelChoices
Then submit event is triggered with answer=1